# Eco-Sync AI — Multi-Agent Resilience Engine

Build a FastAPI + React (TypeScript/Vite) application that scaffolds a 4-stage multi-agent pipeline for Indian market resilience analysis.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend Scaffolding

#### [NEW] [backend/](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/backend/)
- Python project with `requirements.txt` containing: `fastapi`, `uvicorn`, `statsmodels`, `pandas`, `pymcdm`, `langgraph`
- `backend/main.py` — FastAPI app with `/api/health`, `/api/pipeline/status`, `/api/strategies` endpoints
- CORS middleware configured for frontend dev server

---

### Agent Pipeline

#### [NEW] [analyst.py](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/backend/agents/analyst.py)
- VECM (Vector Error Correction Model) tool using `statsmodels.tsa.vector_ar.vecm`
- Accepts time-series data (CPI + NSE indices), returns cointegration analysis results

#### [NEW] [auditor.py](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/backend/agents/auditor.py)
- FOCUS schema mapper for Indian business spend categories
- Maps raw spend data into structured categories (Capex, Opex, Marketing, R&D, Regulatory)

#### [NEW] [jurist.py](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/backend/agents/jurist.py)
- ELECTRE III outranking and VIKOR compromise ranking
- Uses `pymcdm` for multi-criteria decision analysis on strategies

#### [NEW] [controller.py](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/backend/agents/controller.py)
- Unit economics validator: checks CAC, LTV, burn rate, margin thresholds
- Returns pass/fail with detailed breakdown

---

### Mock Data

#### [NEW] [mock_data.py](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/backend/data/mock_data.py)
- Generates 36-month Indian CPI (base ~6%, seasonal variation)
- Generates NSE Nifty 50 index (base ~18000, with drift + volatility)
- Returns pandas DataFrames

---

### Frontend Scaffolding

#### [NEW] [frontend/](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/frontend/)
- Vite + React + TypeScript template
- Install: `tailwindcss`, `@tailwindcss/vite`, `lucide-react`, `axios`

---

### Dashboard Components

#### [NEW] [PipelineProgress.tsx](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/frontend/src/components/PipelineProgress.tsx)
- Horizontal progress bar: Analyst → Auditor → Jurist → Controller
- Each stage shows status (pending/active/complete) with animated transitions

#### [NEW] [StrategyGauntlet.tsx](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/frontend/src/components/StrategyGauntlet.tsx)
- Displays 5 Indian business strategies with VIKOR scores
- Strategies: Tier-2 City Expansion, Raw Material Bulk Buy, Digital-First D2C, Export Diversification, Green Energy Transition

#### [NEW] [App.tsx](file:///home/meitk/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/eco-sync-ai/frontend/src/App.tsx)
- Main dashboard assembling Pipeline + Strategy components
- Health check indicator from backend

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. **Backend health**: `curl http://localhost:8000/api/health` → expect `{"status": "ok"}`
2. **Strategies endpoint**: `curl http://localhost:8000/api/strategies` → expect JSON array of 5 strategies with VIKOR scores
3. **Frontend build**: `npm run build` in frontend/ → should succeed with no errors

### Browser Verification
1. Open `http://localhost:5173` in browser
2. Verify Pipeline Progress bar renders with 4 stages
3. Verify Strategy Gauntlet shows 5 strategies with scores
4. Verify health status indicator shows connected to backend
